('-P3QnL6USmAC', 'A Game of Thrones: The Story Continues Books 1-4: A Game of Thrones, A Clash of Kings, A Storm of Swords, A Feast for Crows (A Song of Ice and Fire)', '', 'HarperCollins UK', '2011-05-11', 'HBO’s hit series A GAME OF THRONES is based on George R R Martin’s internationally bestselling series A SONG OF ICE AND FIRE, the greatest fantasy epic of the modern age.', 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=-P3QnL6USmAC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api', 301961),
