('7vt7tAEACAAJ', 'Green Ninja', 'A Blueprint for Waking the Warrior and Kicking Ass at Life', 'No Publishers found', '2018-01-31', 'Have you ever wondered if \"this is it?\" Have you caught yourself trudging through another mundane day thinking: \"this is not the life I wanted.\" Jim Larsen is a master at waking the dreamer inside and empowering people to achieve a life of meaning and excitement. Green Ninja will walk you step by step through that process, so you don\'t have to look back wishing things had been different.', 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=7vt7tAEACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api', -1),
