('fSj3AwAAQBAJ', 'Double-Team! (Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles)', '', 'Nickelodeon Publishing', '2014-07-08', 'When the villains start to multiply, Nickelodeon\'s Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles are forced to split up. Will two teams be better than one? This Nickelodeon read-along contains audio narration.', 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=fSj3AwAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api', 52417),
