('rYjRAgAAQBAJ', 'Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles: Villain Micro-Series #6 - Hun', '', 'No Published Date', '', 'As the new leader of the Purple Dragons, the villainous Hun joins the war in City Fall! He\'s already making friends in high places and imposing his will on anyone who stands in his way! Hun\'s past will devastate the Turtles\' future!', 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=rYjRAgAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api', 27068),
