('sM3UngEACAAJ', 'The Ninja and the Pastor', '', 'No Publishers found', '2012', 'This is the story of a Jewish man\'s journey to seek truth and to finally find it in his Messiah, Yeshua (Jesus), with the help of an American pastor named Deborah. And it is a story of romance after the shock, grief and trauma of divorce. The Ninja and the Pastor met and were healed together as they walked in His Way.', '', -1),
