('sU8_SaMV0xsC', 'Going Ninja', 'The Eight New Rules for Today\'s Silent Assassins', 'Ulysses Press', '2010-12-01', 'BEING NINJA. DO YOU HAVE WHAT IT TAKES? Not by yourself, that’s for sure. But the brutal, six-week program in Going Ninja will make it happen. Transforming you from a slow-refl exed nobody into a ripped, shuriken-hurling assassin. What is the best way to sever a head with a chopstick? How much personal blood loss is too much? This book shows the way to turn your boring life into a never-ending, sake-filled victory celebration: •Learn to dismember anyone •Wield a ninja sword with confidence •Bone up on the rich history of American ninjas •Tone your arms, neck, jaw and glutes •Get laid every night, in Japanese •Pump up the awesome', 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=sU8_SaMV0xsC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api', -1),
