('xR8PPQAACAAJ', 'Ninja Gaiden Black', 'Prima Official Game Guide', 'No Publishers found', '2005', 'Ninja Gaiden Black Don\'t get dogged! • Maps and walkthrough with item and weapon locations • Crucial strategy for defeating every enemy and boss • Tips for victory in all 46 missions in Master Ninja mode • Training section detailing essential moves, techniques, and weapons • Secret weapons and armlets revealed', 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=xR8PPQAACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api', -1),
