('y1LhoAEACAAJ', 'Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles: Special Edition Movie Novelization (Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles)', '', 'Random House Books for Young Readers', '2014-09-09', 'The Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles try to protect New York from the evil warrior known as the Shredder.', 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=y1LhoAEACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api', -1),
('Y2rStgEACAAJ', 'Ninja Camp', '', 'Running Press Kids', '2019-01-08', 'Pack your bags and grab your gear: you\'re going to Ninja Camp! Listen closely to the ninja master, who will teach you everything you need to know to become a ninja warrior-but it won\'t be easy. You\'ll have to be sly and swift, strong and speedy, and only then will you become a Ninja of the Night! This fun and energetic book will delight and entertain kids and parents alike with its clever, rhyming verse and action-packed depictions of the coolest camp around. For fans of Ninja Red Riding Hood who are looking for a lesson in teamwork and cool stealth skills.', 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=Y2rStgEACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api', -1),
