('YXEdDQAAQBAJ', 'Diary of a 6th Grade Ninja: Diary of a 6th Grade Ninja Book 1', '', 'Allen & Unwin', '2017-01-03', 'It\'s my first day at a new school and the only person I know is my cousin, Zoe (but she might be a little too cool for me). I was just another scrawny kid until a group of ninjas recruited me into their clan. It was a world of trouble I wasn\'t prepared for. This diary is a warning: the life of a ninja is dangerous, scary...and awesome. My name is Chase Cooper, and I\'m a 6th grade ninja.', 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=YXEdDQAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api', -1),
('z36XKg40rdQC', 'Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles - I Can Read', 'The Legend of Yaotl', 'HarperCollins UK', '2007-03-05', 'Long ago an evil man named Yaotl opened an interplanetary portal in search of a magical power. The portal released monsters and magic so powerful that Earth was almost destroyed. This is what happened thousands of years ago. Now he\'s back to do it again.', 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=z36XKg40rdQC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api', -1),
('Z9DUAgAAQBAJ', 'Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles: Black & White Classics Vol. 4', '', 'No Published Date', '', 'The battle between the turtles and the foot escalates further, as Shredder takes the fight to the turtles home front. Devastated by ambush and defeat, the turtles hide away, growing stronger and stronger, until the next time Shredder shows his face, which could be sooner than they think...', 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=Z9DUAgAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api', 135884),
('ZC4QAAAACAAJ', 'Ninja Boy', 'Faded Dreams', 'Dc Comics', '2003', 'After Lord Mikaboshi destroys his clan, Nakio and his friend Sake, aided by the mage Jurojin, set out to kill Mikaboshi, but first they have to get past obstacles including killer spiders, Kura the forest girl, and the Great Devourer.', 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=ZC4QAAAACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api', -1),
